OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,FAn man who washed up on Jersey's
OL,7,Fshores is still detained in the
OL,8,Fisland's prison, six months after
OL,9,Fcompleting his sentence for illegal
OL,10,Fentry.
OL,12,FThe mystery man was found at Rozel Bay
OL,13,Fin September 2024 with no travel
OL,14,Fdocuments and E265 in his pocket, and
OL,15,Fsaid that he had swum to the island
OL,16,Ffrom France.
OL,18,FHe unsuccessfully claimed he was a
OL,19,FBritish man called 'David Henry Law',
OL,20,Fand wished to travel onwards to the UK.
OL,26,@vD@OOk
