CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774800665
OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,F'Law' even quoted William Shakespeare
OL,7,Fin an attempt to prove his citizenship.
OL,9,FIn March 2025, he was sentenced to 15
OL,10,Fmonths in La Moye prison for illegally
OL,11,Fentering the island without leave,
OL,12,Fwhich he was deemed to have served in
OL,13,FSeptember.
OL,15,FBut six months on from the conclusion
OL,16,Fof his prison term, there has been no
OL,17,Findication of when 'Law' will be
OL,18,Freleased, and where he will be
OL,19,Fdeported to.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
