OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774800665
OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,FITV News understands that he has not
OL,7,Fattempted to claim asylum in Jersey,
OL,8,Fand continues to insist he is a
OL,9,FBritish citizen by the name of David
OL,10,FLaw.
OL,12,FITV News also believes the Government
OL,13,Fis trying to obtain travel documents
OL,14,Ffrom various jurisdictions, and
OL,15,Funderstands he's from an "at-risk"
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FJersey's government says it knows the
OL,19,Fman's alias is false but has declined
OL,20,Fto share his true name, age, or
OL,21,Fcountry of origin.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
