FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774800665
OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,FJersey's Minister for Justice and Home
OL,7,FAffairs, Mary Le Hegarat, refused to
OL,8,Fgive further details on what his
OL,9,Ffuture may hold when pressed by ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FShe said: "We do not talk about people
OL,13,Fwho are detained within the prison.
OL,15,F"There is always a plan, but we do not
OL,16,Ftalk about individuals."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
