PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774800665
OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,FPressure is mounting for the man's
OL,7,Frelease as the island's prison nears
OL,8,Fcapacity, with 182 of La Moye's places
OL,9,Foccupied as of October 2025, a number
OL,10,Fwhich has increased year-on-year since
OL,11,F2024.
OL,13,FJournalist Orlando Crowcroft, who had
OL,14,Fextensive written and verbal
OL,15,Fcorrespondence with the man, told ITV
OL,16,FNews about his character.
OL,18,FCrowcroft said: "The first thing I
OL,19,Fnoticed about David is that he's very
OL,20,Feloquent, and he speaks very good
OL,21,FEnglish.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
