PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1774800665
OL,3,CMystery man remains in Jersey jail six
OL,4,Cmonths after completing sentence
OL,6,F"He's in good physical shape, like
OL,7,Fwhen I met him - when he said that he
OL,8,Fhad swum from France, I believed him,
OL,9,Fhe seemed healthy."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
